  "time_ut": 1657423046,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc0 \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba4\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Important information about Prime Minister's house that was set on fire",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A house containing antiques belonging to Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has been set on fire.",
        "Although Ranil Wickremesinghe has served as the prime minister for the most number of times in the country, it is reported that he never moved to Alari House, which was the official residence of the Prime Minister, and even though he went to Alari House for official work, he spent his life in this house.",
        "The largest library was located in the traditional house of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe. There are more books than objects here.",
        "Also, the Prime Minister has issued his last will to donate this house to the Royal College of Colombo after him.",
        "The Prime Minister and his wife Professor Maithiri Wickramasinghe also spent their lives in this house. (a)"
      ],
